mails.title: Meeting Reminder
mails.messageContent: Hi team, just a reminder about our meeting tomorrow at 10 AM. Please be prepared with your updates and any questions you might have. Looking forward to seeing you all there!

mails.title: Project Update
mails.messageContent: Dear team, I wanted to update you on the progress of our current project. We've made significant strides in development and are on track to meet our deadlines. Please review the attached document for detailed information. Let me know if you have any questions or concerns.

mails.title: Request for Proposal
mails.messageContent: Hello, I hope this message finds you well. We are currently seeking proposals for a new project and would like to invite your company to submit a proposal. Please find attached the detailed request and submission guidelines. We look forward to receiving your proposal.

mails.title: Feedback Request
mails.messageContent: Hi team, I'd like to request feedback on the recent client presentation. Your insights and suggestions are valuable as we strive to continuously improve our presentations. Please provide your feedback by the end of this week. Thank you in advance!

mails.title: New Opportunity
mails.messageContent: Dear Alice, we have an exciting new opportunity that I'd like to discuss with you.

mails.title: Product Launch Update
mails.messageContent: Hello Bob, here's the latest update on our upcoming product launch.

mails.title: Marketing Campaign Strategy
mails.messageContent: Hi Eva, let's discuss the marketing campaign strategy for the next quarter.
